*TITR
testing sag calculation
*OLOC
*CONSI
*INSTR
% defining the adjustable sag element
% sag element describes 
*SAGELEMENT sag0 0 2 0 0 1.2345
%*POIN
*CALA
P1_ref 1 0 0
P2_ref -1 0 0
P3_ref 1 1 0
P4_ref -1 1 0
*POIN
P1_sag 1 0 1
P2_sag -1 0 1
P3_sag 1 1 1
P4_sag -1 1 1
*OBSXYZ
P1_sag 1.1 0 4 1 1 1 
P2_sag -1 0 4 1 1 1 
P3_sag 1 1 4 1 1 1 
P4_sag -1 1 4 1 1 1
*SAGCONNECT P1_ref P1_sag sag0
*SAGCONNECT P2_ref P2_sag sag0
*SAGCONNECT P3_ref P3_sag sag0
*SAGCONNECT P4_ref P4_sag sag0
*END
